WEBVTT

00:00:00.732 --> 00:00:01.672
vi azoy

00:00:02.167 --> 00:00:03.022
bay

00:00:03.753 --> 00:00:08.709
NAOMI LOEBEL, THE SURVIVOR IS SARAH TAUB, AND THE LANGUAGE IS YIDDISH.

00:00:10.857 --> 00:00:14.464
zogst mir, un- undz ho'mir frier geredt vegn

00:00:14.806 --> 00:00:17.940
ayer, ir zent geven in Bukarest...

00:00:17.877 --> 00:00:18.707
yo,

00:00:18.063 --> 00:00:19.560
mit ayer khaverte?

00:00:20.544 --> 00:00:21.365
yo.

00:00:21.539 --> 00:00:23.340
vu zent ir gevezn dort?

00:00:23.817 --> 00:00:32.689
und dort hob ikh mikh fardingen far a meshores.

00:00:34.246 --> 00:00:37.751
un ikh bin geven bayn a mishpokhe

00:00:38.431 --> 00:00:42.240
a meshores, un kh'hob zeyer shver gearbet.

00:00:43.055 --> 00:00:47.758
ikh bin geven tsugevoynt tsu arbetn, ober nisht azoy shver.

00:00:48.826 --> 00:00:53.951
un zey hobn mir gegen aza shvere arbet

00:00:54.024 --> 00:00:56.111
vos ikh hob nisht gekent makhn.

00:00:58.546 --> 00:01:00.988
ikh zol putsn...

00:01:02.140 --> 00:01:04.025
shlekhte mentshn.

00:01:04.739 --> 00:01:08.599
nisht mit genug yidish harts.

00:01:08.992 --> 00:01:11.737
ikh zol putsn parket.

00:01:12.384 --> 00:01:14.387
ir veyst vos iz parket?

00:01:15.657 --> 00:01:18.875
un dos hot men gebroykht putsn

00:01:19.269 --> 00:01:20.833
mit benzin.

00:01:22.239 --> 00:01:26.790
un mayn guf hot nisht fartrogn dem benzin.

00:01:27.234 --> 00:01:29.642
se iz mir shlekht geven.

00:01:30.052 --> 00:01:32.325
se iz mir zeyer shlekht geven.

00:01:32.617 --> 00:01:33.945
un ikh hob gezogt,

00:01:34.085 --> 00:01:36.172
"ikh ken arbetn,

00:01:36.599 --> 00:01:39.176
ober deys ken ikh nisht makhn."

00:01:42.354 --> 00:01:45.572
un hot men gezogt, "gut."

00:01:47.281 --> 00:01:50.364
un me hot mir gegebn tsu vashn vesh.

00:01:51.382 --> 00:01:53.368
zeyer shver geven.

00:01:53.660 --> 00:01:57.232
se iz geven direkt royberish.

00:01:57.609 --> 00:02:01.012
un ikh bin geven a yung meydl,

00:02:01.017 --> 00:02:02.582
vi alt zent ir geven?

00:02:04.595 --> 00:02:07.037
zibetsn, akhtsn yor.

00:02:17.622 --> 00:02:20.554
un ikh bin krank gevorn.

00:02:21.689 --> 00:02:23.895
kh'hob bakumen ulkus.

00:02:25.503 --> 00:02:27.474
un dos ulkus,

00:02:27.474 --> 00:02:32.366
bin ikh avek tsum dokter.

00:02:34.464 --> 00:02:37.310
un der dokter hot gezogt ikh bin

00:02:37.788 --> 00:02:41.630
tsu yung me zol mikh operirn.

00:02:44.133 --> 00:02:47.520
un dernokh dem bin ikh krank gevorn

00:02:47.542 --> 00:02:49.511
mit gal shteyner.

00:02:51.339 --> 00:02:54.034
un se iz geven fun Amerike,

00:02:54.309 --> 00:02:56.407
di mame's a bruder,

00:02:56.407 --> 00:02:57.544
a dokter.

00:02:58.190 --> 00:03:00.651
un er hot gezogt men broykh,

00:03:00.651 --> 00:03:03.315
ikh broykh mikh lozn operirn.

00:03:03.505 --> 00:03:05.947
von azoy ken men nisht lebn.

00:03:06.965 --> 00:03:07.905
ikh hob ge-,

00:03:07.927 --> 00:03:09.204
SLICHA,

00:03:09.783 --> 00:03:11.128
gebrokhn,

00:03:11.133 --> 00:03:13.693
un ikh bin krank geven.

00:03:15.284 --> 00:03:17.119
un men hot mikh operirt.

00:03:18.355 --> 00:03:22.519
un nokh vos men hot mikh operirt,

00:03:22.777 --> 00:03:24.392
hot er mir gezogt

00:03:24.785 --> 00:03:27.530
az, hob ikh gezogt,

00:03:27.873 --> 00:03:30.365
vel ikh shoyn mer nisht hobn keyn

00:03:30.421 --> 00:03:32.764
krempfn, bay di gal,

00:03:32.764 --> 00:03:35.276
von dos makht groyse krempfn.

00:03:36.091 --> 00:03:39.140
hot er gezogt, efsher neyn.

00:03:40.242 --> 00:03:45.604
von me hot di gal in gantsn aroysgenumen.

00:03:45.963 --> 00:03:49.772
ober ikh bin shoyn alt geven tsvontsik,

00:03:50.199 --> 00:03:52.708
efsher a bisl mer,

00:03:53.793 --> 00:03:56.758
un er zogt az bay dem gil,

00:03:57.050 --> 00:03:59.323
ken di gal, di,

00:03:59.379 --> 00:04:02.158
shteyner tsurikkumen,

00:04:02.281 --> 00:04:04.689
azoy az se iz beser

00:04:04.728 --> 00:04:08.975
az men nemt, az men hot aroysgenumen di gal.

00:04:09.841 --> 00:04:13.009
bin ikh geven BESEDER a bisl tsayt.

00:04:15.258 --> 00:04:20.130
un ikh bin avek fun Bukarest.

00:04:20.253 --> 00:04:23.302
in Kloyznborg hot men mikh operirt.

00:04:26.041 --> 00:04:31.453
un ikh denk nisht azoy BEDIYUK,

00:04:33.719 --> 00:04:38.321
ikh hob gehat a shvester in Tshekhay.

00:04:39.777 --> 00:04:43.957
deys iz geven in Trentshenteplits.

00:04:44.131 --> 00:04:46.033
ir hot gehert derfun?

00:04:46.662 --> 00:04:48.649
dos iz vayt,

00:04:48.856 --> 00:04:50.252
in Tshekhay.

00:04:51.421 --> 00:04:54.217
un di mume iz geshtorbn.

00:04:55.117 --> 00:04:59.516
un zi hot shoyn nisht gekent zayn dort, mitn feter.

00:05:00.247 --> 00:05:02.334
al pi din undzerer.

00:05:02.660 --> 00:05:04.174
azoy az,

00:05:04.567 --> 00:05:07.430
zi hot ge-, zi hot geshribn,

00:05:08.060 --> 00:05:09.945
nisht tsu mir,

00:05:10.321 --> 00:05:12.679
tsum tatn's bruder.

00:05:13.190 --> 00:05:15.440
az zi broykh d-,

00:05:15.440 --> 00:05:19.159
von m- der dem tatn's bruder

00:05:19.197 --> 00:05:21.825
hot geshribn az der tate

00:05:21.897 --> 00:05:23.580
iz geshtorbn.

00:05:24.040 --> 00:05:25.008
hot s- a-,

00:05:25.008 --> 00:05:29.030
ikh veys nisht zi, ober der feter, hot tsurikgeshribn,

00:05:29.204 --> 00:05:33.469
az zi broykh nokh dort blaybn dray khadoshim.

00:05:33.760 --> 00:05:36.742
von zi broykh endikn dem bagrunt.

00:05:38.030 --> 00:05:39.274
dos heyst,

00:05:39.835 --> 00:05:42.817
ERETTSEGI oyf ungarish.

00:05:43.109 --> 00:05:45.905
azoy, nokh dem iz zi aheymgekumen.

00:05:46.332 --> 00:05:51.592
ober me ho'mir zikh a sakh a sakh tsayt nisht gezen, a sakh yorn.

00:05:52.914 --> 00:05:57.617
un ven me ho'mir zikh gezen, ho'mir zikh nisht derkont.

00:06:00.592 --> 00:06:03.152
ikh hob nisht gevust zi iz mayn shvester,

00:06:03.646 --> 00:06:06.729
un zi hot nisht gevust ikh bin ir shvester.

00:06:08.320 --> 00:06:11.522
azoy ze'mir geven a bisele, a por teg,

00:06:11.938 --> 00:06:13.208
bayn tatn's...

00:06:13.208 --> 00:06:16.044
zi iz ongekumen fun Tshekhay.

00:06:16.488 --> 00:06:18.592
tsum tatn's bruder,

00:06:20.150 --> 00:06:23.722
mit a PAKIT fun UNCLE,

00:06:25.077 --> 00:06:27.536
un me hot mir tsu visn gegen

00:06:28.385 --> 00:06:32.548
az zi iz dort, bin ikh geganen. ze'mir geven tsuzamen

00:06:34.865 --> 00:06:36.592
dray, fir tog.

00:06:36.592 --> 00:06:38.640
tsvey tog, ikh gedenk nisht.

00:06:39.185 --> 00:06:44.546
azoy, zi hot nisht gekent ungarish, un nisht rumenish,

00:06:44.855 --> 00:06:47.854
nor yidish, ober oykh tsebrokhn

00:06:48.078 --> 00:06:52.623
zi hot geredt di loshn

00:06:52.623 --> 00:06:55.042
vos se iz dort, vos me hot dort geredt

00:06:55.132 --> 00:06:57.793
vos zi hot gelernt in shul.

00:06:57.865 --> 00:07:00.442
yidish hot zi geredt a bisl.

00:07:02.590 --> 00:07:05.876
un dernokh dem ho'mir zikh vayter tseteylt.

00:07:09.442 --> 00:07:11.647
un nokh etlekhe yorn

00:07:12.732 --> 00:07:14.735
hot zi khasene gehat,

00:07:15.635 --> 00:07:19.174
un zi hot gevoynt in Bukarest.

00:07:19.499 --> 00:07:23.139
bin ikh tsurikgegangen oyf Bukarest.

00:07:25.692 --> 00:07:28.370
un ikh hob ongefangen

00:07:28.612 --> 00:07:30.244
tsu lernen

00:07:30.485 --> 00:07:33.332
a krankn-shvester, ikh hob shoyn gehat

00:07:33.927 --> 00:07:35.593
a shtikl heym.

00:07:36.948 --> 00:07:38.580
ikh hob shoyn gehat a

00:07:38.770 --> 00:07:41.162
a va-, a varemkeyt.

00:07:42.635 --> 00:07:46.258
un bayn,

00:07:46.330 --> 00:07:51.422
ikh bin shoyn elter geven ven ikh hob ongefangen tsu lernen shvesters,

00:07:51.730 --> 00:07:55.134
tsvishn tsvey un dray un tsvontsik yor.

00:07:57.249 --> 00:07:59.589
un ikh hob gelernt a bisl,

00:07:59.797 --> 00:08:03.454
un me hot mikh aroysgevorfn, nisht nor mikh,

00:08:03.610 --> 00:08:06.255
oykh andere yidishe meydlekh.

00:08:06.395 --> 00:08:08.955
in velkhe yor iz dos geven, ir gedenkt?

00:08:11.913 --> 00:08:13.899
ikh denk nisht azoy gut.

00:08:14.613 --> 00:08:17.156
ir zent alt geven dray un tsvontsik yor?

00:08:18.393 --> 00:08:21.105
dray un fir un tsvontsik.

00:08:21.042 --> 00:08:24.514
dos iz beerekh in fir un draysik un in finef un draysik.

00:08:25.042 --> 00:08:26.083
vi azoy?

00:08:25.852 --> 00:08:28.834
in fir un draysik un in finef un draysik.

00:08:27.809 --> 00:08:28.903
yo, yo.

00:08:28.903 --> 00:08:30.352
azoy gatung.

00:08:32.416 --> 00:08:35.449
un ikh hob gezen se geyt mir nisht.

00:08:37.495 --> 00:08:40.950
hob ikh gevolt lernen

00:08:42.288 --> 00:08:43.717
far a kekhn.

00:08:46.000 --> 00:08:50.349
nu, deys iz oykh nisht gut geven, von ikh hob gezen

00:08:50.979 --> 00:08:53.201
dort arbet men mit

00:08:53.425 --> 00:08:55.125
khazer fleyshn.

00:08:57.104 --> 00:09:00.322
hob ikh nisht, ikh hob nisht gevolt blaybn.

00:09:00.817 --> 00:09:05.047
me iz geven tsufridn, me hot gezogt az ikh lern gut,

00:09:05.592 --> 00:09:08.810
ober ikh hob gezen, me hot arayngebrengt

00:09:09.305 --> 00:09:10.869
kh- khazer,

00:09:11.330 --> 00:09:13.552
hob ikh nisht gevolt lernen.

00:09:16.325 --> 00:09:17.113
un,

00:09:18.620 --> 00:09:20.707
vos hob ikh nor geton?

00:09:22.720 --> 00:09:24.572
ikh gedenk shoyn nisht.

00:09:26.399 --> 00:09:28.244
von ikh hob geton epes.

00:09:28.244 --> 00:09:28.892
yo,

00:09:29.656 --> 00:09:31.625
ikh hob oyfgepast

00:09:31.917 --> 00:09:33.752
oyf tsvey kinder.

00:09:37.199 --> 00:09:41.615
ober se iz zeyer, me hot zeyer veynik getsolt.

00:09:42.211 --> 00:09:44.957
un dortn hob ikh oykh gebroykht

00:09:45.839 --> 00:09:48.230
gants shver arbetn.

00:09:49.501 --> 00:09:55.166
se iz geven demolts in in Bukarest a sakh antisemitizm kegn di yidn?

00:09:55.306 --> 00:09:56.195
vi azoy?

00:09:56.065 --> 00:09:59.047
in Bukarest, ven ir zent geven dort yetst,

00:09:59.255 --> 00:10:01.933
iz geven a sakh ANTISHEMYUT?

00:10:02.275 --> 00:10:04.920
se iz nisht geven geferlekh.

00:10:05.229 --> 00:10:09.932
von in Bukarest iz geven a sakh komunistn.

00:10:11.928 --> 00:10:15.855
un se iz nisht shver geven unter di komunistn,

00:10:16.096 --> 00:10:23.027
nor ven di daytshn zenen,

00:10:23.234 --> 00:10:26.435
di daytshn zenen, zey hobn nisht gekent

00:10:26.727 --> 00:10:31.076
in gantsn araynkumen keyn Bukarest.

00:10:31.942 --> 00:10:35.329
di rusn hobn zey tsurik geshtupt.

00:10:35.890 --> 00:10:38.315
iz zeyer a sakh daytshn

00:10:38.810 --> 00:10:41.876
zenen derharget gevorn in Bukarest.

00:10:42.033 --> 00:10:43.243
armey.

00:10:44.716 --> 00:10:46.399
azoy az

00:10:48.310 --> 00:10:50.617
ikh ken mikh shoyn nisht dermanen,

00:10:50.875 --> 00:10:51.545
yo,

00:10:53.474 --> 00:10:55.545
se iz mir shver geven

00:10:55.752 --> 00:10:57.519
mit kinder,

00:10:58.300 --> 00:11:04.168
dey arbet, von se iz nisht geven nor ikh zol mikh basheftikn mit di kinder,

00:11:04.240 --> 00:11:07.931
me hot mir gegen oykh gresere arbet.

00:11:09.269 --> 00:11:12.521
un ikh hob nisht gekent endikn.

00:11:13.707 --> 00:11:18.545
voynung hot men mir oykh gegebn, ikh hob dort geshlofn un gegesn.

00:11:18.736 --> 00:11:20.250
un ikh hob gekokht.

00:11:21.588 --> 00:11:26.409
un ikh hob gebroykht, biz oyf der nakht shpet arbetn.

00:11:27.089 --> 00:11:31.235
un se iz mir nisht, ikh bin nokh nisht geven azoy

00:11:31.392 --> 00:11:34.425
a sakh tsayt, nokhn NITUACH.

00:11:36.590 --> 00:11:38.222
azoy az,

00:11:40.353 --> 00:11:42.204
ikh bin gegangen,

00:11:42.969 --> 00:11:45.697
a froy hot mir ongetrogn

00:11:46.006 --> 00:11:49.528
ikh zol bay ir biglen.

00:11:50.680 --> 00:11:54.323
un zi hot mir nokh farshafn koynim

00:11:54.323 --> 00:11:56.160
vi ikh zol biglen.

00:11:56.637 --> 00:12:00.362
dort hot men dokh nisht gebiglt, se iz nokh nisht geven

00:12:00.451 --> 00:12:04.448
modern, keyn CHASHMAL bigl-ayzn.

00:12:04.448 --> 00:12:05.998
mit koyln.

00:12:06.914 --> 00:12:09.434
un se iz mir zeyer nisht gut geven.

00:12:09.434 --> 00:12:12.410
ikh hob gehalt dos fentster ofn un

00:12:12.972 --> 00:12:14.334
ikh hob es gemakht.

00:12:15.571 --> 00:12:19.076
un di froy iz geven zeyer a guter mentsh,

00:12:19.857 --> 00:12:22.620
un zi hot mir zeyer gevolt helfn.

00:12:22.878 --> 00:12:24.797
hot zi gezogt tsu mir,

00:12:25.443 --> 00:12:27.058
"her oys, Sara,

00:12:27.637 --> 00:12:33.875
mayn man arbet in a groysn akhsan fun oyps.

00:12:34.049 --> 00:12:35.666
un dort iz do,

00:12:35.666 --> 00:12:40.558
er zukht a froy, a mentsh,

00:12:40.597 --> 00:12:43.528
zol knakn nisn.

00:12:45.997 --> 00:12:48.675
me get aroys nisn,

00:12:49.085 --> 00:12:54.142
un ikh gedenk nisht BEDIYUK vifl protsentn

00:12:54.367 --> 00:12:57.551
hot men opgerekhnt der sholekhts,

00:12:57.674 --> 00:13:00.875
un dernokh dem dos fun inevendik.

00:13:01.285 --> 00:13:06.005
un me hot mir gegebn tsen kilo nisn.

00:13:07.090 --> 00:13:09.482
un dos hob ikh opgeputst,

00:13:09.622 --> 00:13:13.498
un di sholekhts hob ikh avekgevorfn,

00:13:14.634 --> 00:13:18.105
un di,

00:13:18.414 --> 00:13:21.041
dos inevendikste, di mandlen,

00:13:21.164 --> 00:13:23.100
hot men opgemostn

00:13:23.122 --> 00:13:25.749
un me iz geven zeyer tsufridn,

00:13:25.771 --> 00:13:27.844
vos se iz mer geven

00:13:27.844 --> 00:13:30.575
vifl se hot gebroykht zayn.

00:13:30.783 --> 00:13:33.579
un ikh hob nisht aropgenumen gornisht.

00:13:33.787 --> 00:13:39.266
un ikh hob nisht genumen in moyl a peyre, oder epes on a brokhe.

00:13:39.676 --> 00:13:42.202
un ikh hob gelernt

00:13:42.629 --> 00:13:49.931
az iber a geganvete zakh tor men nisht makhn a brokhe, azoy ikh hob es nisht ongerirt.

00:13:50.898 --> 00:13:57.035
un dernokh dem hob ikh gezogt tsu der froy,

00:13:57.699 --> 00:14:00.261
"BESEDER, ikh vel es makhn,

00:14:00.261 --> 00:14:02.334
ikh vil es makhn."

00:14:02.508 --> 00:14:04.699
"di tsen kilo,"

00:14:04.699 --> 00:14:06.097
hot zi gezogt,

00:14:06.406 --> 00:14:08.240
"makh es do bay mir."

00:14:10.186 --> 00:14:12.949
un zi hot gezogt az zi vet redn

00:14:13.477 --> 00:14:16.273
mit ir a kuzine,

00:14:16.312 --> 00:14:18.602
az zi zol mir gebn voynung,

00:14:19.248 --> 00:14:20.947
un zi zol,

00:14:21.104 --> 00:14:25.217
dort zol ikh makhn dey nisn.

00:14:26.082 --> 00:14:26.752
nu,

00:14:27.230 --> 00:14:29.284
se iz gezogt in gemakht.

00:14:29.508 --> 00:14:30.872
vi lang hot ir gearbet?

00:14:30.872 --> 00:14:31.562
far dem?

00:14:32.090 --> 00:14:33.958
dray a halb yor.

00:14:34.520 --> 00:14:36.523
un vos hot ir geton nokh dem?

00:14:38.300 --> 00:14:39.546
nokh dem...

00:14:39.546 --> 00:14:41.231
ikh denk nisht.

00:14:44.139 --> 00:14:46.479
ikh denk nisht vos ikh hob geton.

00:14:46.923 --> 00:14:49.399
nor deys hot zikh oyfgehert.

00:14:50.973 --> 00:14:53.567
ven di milkhome hot oysgebrokhn,

00:14:54.162 --> 00:14:55.777
in in Bukarest,

00:14:56.575 --> 00:14:57.178
ah!

00:15:00.744 --> 00:15:04.367
ikh bin geven bay mayn shvester.

00:15:07.966 --> 00:15:12.602
ikh mish oys a bisele, ikh derman mikh nisht BEDIYUK.

00:15:14.817 --> 00:15:16.972
di milkhome hot oyfge-

00:15:18.310 --> 00:15:20.972
oysgebrokhn in Bukarest,

00:15:21.601 --> 00:15:26.119
ven ikh bin gekumen fun Kloyznborg tsurik

00:15:26.495 --> 00:15:28.582
oyf Bukarest, yo.

00:15:30.730 --> 00:15:34.134
un ikh denk nisht BEDIYUK vos kh'hob geton,

00:15:34.814 --> 00:15:36.615
nor, dernokh dem,

00:15:37.261 --> 00:15:38.083
ah, yo!

00:15:39.404 --> 00:15:42.487
kh'hob gemakht METAPEL

00:15:42.678 --> 00:15:44.394
bayn an alte froy.

00:15:48.871 --> 00:15:52.697
un me hot genug veynik batsolt.

00:15:53.512 --> 00:15:57.388
ikh bin tsufridn geven, kh'hob gegesn dort, un

00:15:57.477 --> 00:16:00.695
dort gesh- dort gevoynt,

00:16:01.426 --> 00:16:03.547
un mayn shvester hot gezogt,

00:16:03.957 --> 00:16:08.981
"her oys, s'iz beser zolst kumen lebn bay mir."

00:16:09.661 --> 00:16:11.928
me zol mir zayn tsuzamen.

00:16:11.928 --> 00:16:13.250
zi

00:16:13.525 --> 00:16:14.786
un n-

00:16:14.859 --> 00:16:17.250
dervayl hot zi khasene gehat.

00:16:18.250 --> 00:16:23.814
un ikh bin geven bay ir, bay mayn shvester,

00:16:24.342 --> 00:16:26.514
un se iz geven zeyer gut,

00:16:26.570 --> 00:16:29.197
kh'hob a sakh gebroykht arbetn,

00:16:29.320 --> 00:16:32.792
von der shvester's man hot gehat a gesheft,

00:16:33.151 --> 00:16:36.369
un mayn shvester iz geven in gesheft.

00:16:36.610 --> 00:16:39.896
un ikh hob gefirt di virtshaft.

00:16:40.087 --> 00:16:43.535
mit a goy, a goye, iz oykh geven bay di

00:16:43.535 --> 00:16:45.364
shvere arbetn.

00:16:46.989 --> 00:16:52.654
un fun zey, fun mayn shvester,

00:16:52.878 --> 00:16:55.894
hob ikh dernokh dem khasene gehat.

00:16:58.295 --> 00:17:01.108
un se hot zikh geendikt mayne

00:17:02.429 --> 00:17:04.955
mayne groyse shverikeytn.

00:17:05.129 --> 00:17:06.727
nor nokh dem,

00:17:07.340 --> 00:17:10.220
ikh hob gevoynt bay mayn shvester,

00:17:11.356 --> 00:17:14.051
biz a dray yor, azoy gatung.

00:17:14.275 --> 00:17:17.797
ober mit mayn man iz nisht geven BESEDER.

00:17:17.667 --> 00:17:19.502
ober, in di milkhome,

00:17:20.469 --> 00:17:24.260
vu zent ir geven ven di daytshn zenen gekumen oyf Bukarest?

00:17:23.911 --> 00:17:24.902
in Bukarest.

00:17:24.502 --> 00:17:25.307
*

00:17:25.345 --> 00:17:26.859
vu zent ir geven?

00:17:26.544 --> 00:17:28.175
bay mayn shvester.

00:17:30.501 --> 00:17:32.040
bin ikh geven.

00:17:30.540 --> 00:17:31.469
ir zent...

00:17:32.264 --> 00:17:37.796
un un, dort iz nisht geven keyn, me hot nisht deportirt keyn yidn fun dort?

00:17:38.272 --> 00:17:40.055
me hot deportirt,

00:17:40.229 --> 00:17:43.633
ober nisht, oyf Daytshland.

00:17:44.785 --> 00:17:48.577
oyf an ander plats, Transnitsrie

00:17:49.038 --> 00:17:50.839
hot dos geheysn.

00:17:51.637 --> 00:17:55.091
dort hot men oykh zeyer groyse tsores gemakht.

00:17:55.754 --> 00:17:59.597
dort iz nisht geven keyn kremator.

00:18:02.386 --> 00:18:04.777
di yidn zenen geshtorbn,

00:18:05.643 --> 00:18:08.939
me hot oykh geharget, un oykh geshtorbn,

00:18:08.939 --> 00:18:13.502
far hunger, far kelt, far tsores.

00:18:15.599 --> 00:18:18.800
un se iz geven, me hot gefunen,

00:18:18.957 --> 00:18:21.551
nokh vos di daytshn zenen avek,

00:18:21.961 --> 00:18:25.534
di daytshn zenen avek, von di rusn

00:18:25.944 --> 00:18:27.434
hob zey ge-,

00:18:27.434 --> 00:18:28.892
aroysgeshtupt.

00:18:29.032 --> 00:18:30.883
un a sakh geharget.

00:18:32.677 --> 00:18:34.714
un zey zenen avek.

00:18:35.647 --> 00:18:38.983
vu zent ir geven biz di sof fun di milkhome?

00:18:39.376 --> 00:18:41.010
in Bukarest.

00:18:41.047 --> 00:18:42.679
vos hot ir getun demolts?

00:18:43.527 --> 00:18:45.581
demolts hob ikh gelernt,

00:18:46.649 --> 00:18:48.112
a shvester,

00:18:48.674 --> 00:18:51.133
un demolts bin ikh gevorn

00:18:51.982 --> 00:18:55.132
bin tsu mayn shvester gegangen,

00:18:55.441 --> 00:18:58.642
befor ikh bin gegangen tsu mayn shvester,

00:18:59.069 --> 00:19:03.857
ho- bin ikh geven a MITAPELET bayn an an eltere froy.

00:19:04.503 --> 00:19:06.182
zeyer UNK.

00:19:06.055 --> 00:19:10.286
ir hot gelernt tsu zayn a shvester in a shpitol zent ir geven?

00:19:10.949 --> 00:19:13.594
yo, ober se iz geven

00:19:13.852 --> 00:19:16.142
zeyer a shvere tsayt.

00:19:16.400 --> 00:19:19.601
von di shvesters fun shpitol

00:19:19.927 --> 00:19:22.858
hot men ales avekgenumen.

00:19:22.897 --> 00:19:26.284
di ge- oysgelernt shvesters,

00:19:26.440 --> 00:19:29.254
azoy az undz, TALMIDOT,

00:19:29.326 --> 00:19:31.694
hot men genumen

00:19:31.694 --> 00:19:34.704
in MACHLAKAL- in di MAKHLAKOT.

00:19:34.929 --> 00:19:36.409
me hot genumen

00:19:37.797 --> 00:19:40.779
pensyenerte shvesters,

00:19:41.037 --> 00:19:47.242
vos zey zoln undz lernen vos me ho'mir tsu ton

00:19:47.956 --> 00:19:49.554
mit di kranke.

00:19:49.728 --> 00:19:53.300
von in der shul hot men nisht gekent lernen.

00:19:54.048 --> 00:19:55.174
diuretik.

00:20:01.692 --> 00:20:04.708
se iz zeyer, zeyer geven a

00:20:05.472 --> 00:20:06.902
a groyse ruml.

00:20:08.712 --> 00:20:11.930
ur ir zen- ir zent geven dort a shvester in di shpitol?

00:20:12.847 --> 00:20:16.068
ikh bin nisht geven keyn oysgelernte shvester.

00:20:14.422 --> 00:20:17.486
yo, ober ir hot gearbet als shvester.

00:20:16.071 --> 00:20:17.580
yo, yo.

00:20:17.580 --> 00:20:20.393
ikh hob gearbet biz in a tsayt.

00:20:20.829 --> 00:20:27.202
ober se iz viderum aroysgegangen a bafel

00:20:27.275 --> 00:20:28.704
az me broykh

00:20:29.064 --> 00:20:33.109
ale MITAPELE, shvester, ales broykh men

00:20:33.198 --> 00:20:35.437
avekgeyn oyf Daytshland.

00:20:37.332 --> 00:20:39.538
un ikh bin geven

00:20:43.120 --> 00:20:44.432
mit a

00:20:45.129 --> 00:20:47.334
⟨CHALUT⟩ fun di arbet,

00:20:47.761 --> 00:20:50.000
mit a tikhl oyfn kop,

00:20:52.334 --> 00:20:55.974
un ikh bin durkhgeshprungen a ployt.

00:20:58.038 --> 00:21:02.201
un dort iz geven TAXI, un ikh bin avekgeforn

00:21:03.084 --> 00:21:04.918
tsu mayn shvester.

00:21:06.087 --> 00:21:08.090
un mayn shvester hot,

00:21:08.264 --> 00:21:11.128
un mayn shvoger, zeyer moyre gehat.

00:21:11.724 --> 00:21:13.997
von me vet mikh kumen zukhn.

00:21:14.930 --> 00:21:16.393
fun shpitol.

00:21:16.702 --> 00:21:17.753
me zol

00:21:17.753 --> 00:21:20.932
ikh zol oykh avekgeyn, vi di iberike

00:21:22.254 --> 00:21:26.351
meydlekh, nisht zeyer geven a sakh, ober shikses

00:21:26.351 --> 00:21:28.239
hot men oykh genumen.

00:21:30.067 --> 00:21:31.718
un se iz geven

00:21:31.718 --> 00:21:34.432
zeyer a fayne froy, a shokhnte,

00:21:34.640 --> 00:21:38.499
a daytshe, un zi hot gezogt

00:21:38.639 --> 00:21:44.557
ikh zol zayn bay ir bahaltn, zi hot mir gegen a plats,

00:21:45.507 --> 00:21:49.681
un bayn undz iz di

00:21:49.738 --> 00:21:53.737
UNK, azoy vi se iz do, bayn undz, dort nisht do keyn

00:21:54.552 --> 00:21:58.547
iberal keyn tsentrale heytsung,

00:22:01.066 --> 00:22:03.052
un zi hot gehat a

00:22:03.125 --> 00:22:05.870
a groyse kamer mit holts.

00:22:06.145 --> 00:22:08.030
un me hot dos holts

00:22:08.103 --> 00:22:10.494
avekgenumen fun di vant,

00:22:10.854 --> 00:22:13.127
me hot gearbet dermit,

00:22:13.773 --> 00:22:17.717
un mayn shvoger zol zikh mien hot oykh gearbet dermit,

00:22:18.177 --> 00:22:21.075
un me hot mir dort gemakht a plats

00:22:21.114 --> 00:22:23.640
vu ikh zol hobn a geleger.

00:22:24.016 --> 00:22:26.897
un ikh bin dort geven bahaltn

00:22:27.273 --> 00:22:29.681
fir, finef khadoshim.

00:22:30.901 --> 00:22:33.140
ver hot aykh gegebn tsu esn?

00:22:33.466 --> 00:22:35.132
ven ir zent geven bahaltn?

00:22:35.694 --> 00:22:38.372
se iz geven groyse tsores.

00:22:39.271 --> 00:22:42.067
dey froy hot mir arayngebrengt

00:22:42.376 --> 00:22:47.501
harte ayer, gekokht, un kartofl in der sholekhts.

00:22:47.759 --> 00:22:51.011
un mayn shvester hot moyre gehat

00:22:51.354 --> 00:22:53.930
zi zol kumen, zi zol mir brengen,

00:22:54.054 --> 00:22:55.432
LIFAMIM,

00:22:56.568 --> 00:23:00.984
hot zi zikh ongeshtrengt, un zi hot gebrengt tsu der froy

00:23:01.765 --> 00:23:02.773
esn,

00:23:03.267 --> 00:23:09.320
un dey froy hot es mir arayngebrengt, ober zeyer zeltn, ikh hob gehungert.

00:23:11.435 --> 00:23:13.809
ober se iz nisht geven keyn breyre.

00:23:14.979 --> 00:23:17.690
un vos hot ir geton dort a gantsn tog?

00:23:19.400 --> 00:23:20.779
ikh veys nisht.

00:23:21.003 --> 00:23:22.348
ikh hob geveynt.

00:23:24.884 --> 00:23:31.815
von leyenen hob ikh nisht gekent, se iz nisht geven likht, se iz geven zeyer azoy...

00:23:32.630 --> 00:23:33.620
tunkl.

00:23:32.984 --> 00:23:35.892
oyf a plats vos se iz nisht do keyn

00:23:35.892 --> 00:23:37.755
fentster, se iz nor,

00:23:39.009 --> 00:23:41.214
se iz zeyer shver geven.

00:23:42.805 --> 00:23:45.804
dey froy hot a mol geredt tsu aykh dort?

00:23:46.754 --> 00:23:52.318
nisht zi, von se hot nokh gevoynt dort in hoyf emetser,

00:23:52.711 --> 00:23:56.708
un zi hot moyre gehat, se iz nisht geven ikh bin in

00:23:56.708 --> 00:24:00.097
sekone, iz zi dokh oykh geven in sekone,

00:24:00.322 --> 00:24:03.725
az me hot gefunen az a goy bahalt a yid,

00:24:03.865 --> 00:24:06.004
hot men zofort geshosn.

00:24:07.814 --> 00:24:08.434
yo.

00:24:08.793 --> 00:24:12.804
zi hot gehat tsvey, dray tekhter, dey froy.

00:24:12.978 --> 00:24:16.972
un di tekhter hobn nisht gevust az ikh leb dort.

00:24:18.462 --> 00:24:19.824
az ikh bin dort.

00:24:20.352 --> 00:24:24.397
un di tekhter hobn gearbet, zey zenen nisht geven in der heym.

00:24:25.567 --> 00:24:29.426
UNK in der fri avek un oyf der nakht iz men gekumen.

00:24:29.988 --> 00:24:32.750
ir gedenkt vi azoy di froy hot geheysn?

00:24:32.772 --> 00:24:33.459
yo.

00:24:33.532 --> 00:24:34.438
vi azoy?

00:24:35.759 --> 00:24:39.214
ir PRATI nomen veys ikh nisht,

00:24:39.759 --> 00:24:43.139
nor ir mishpokhe nomen hobn geheysn

00:24:43.139 --> 00:24:44.107
HOBERT.

00:24:45.310 --> 00:24:46.149
HOBERT.

00:24:47.217 --> 00:24:48.022
yo.

00:24:47.740 --> 00:24:51.819
zi hot aykh bahaltn oyf fir, finef khadoshim.

00:24:55.334 --> 00:24:57.253
far vos hot zi dos geton?

00:24:57.747 --> 00:24:59.075
vos klert ir?

00:24:58.152 --> 00:25:01.067
far vos, zi iz geven a guter mentsh,

00:25:02.067 --> 00:25:04.762
un zi hot mikh lib gehat,

00:25:05.847 --> 00:25:08.576
un zi hot gehat rakhmones.

00:25:12.226 --> 00:25:12.896
yo.

00:25:14.032 --> 00:25:16.794
zi hot arayn- zi hot gehat a hunt,

00:25:17.221 --> 00:25:20.692
hot zi dem hunt arayngenumen bayn ir in shtub,

00:25:21.102 --> 00:25:25.198
der hunt zol nisht biln. ikh zol mikh nisht dershrekn

00:25:25.321 --> 00:25:27.965
az me kumt mikh zukhn.

00:25:28.595 --> 00:25:30.024
ir farshteyt mir?

00:25:31.447 --> 00:25:35.492
iz zi geven a daytshke, zi iz nisht geven fun Daytshland,

00:25:35.649 --> 00:25:37.669
zi iz geven fun a

00:25:39.327 --> 00:25:41.594
a shtot, se hot geheysn

00:25:41.594 --> 00:25:42.967
Brashoy.

00:25:43.310 --> 00:25:45.853
nor zi hot khasene gehat

00:25:46.567 --> 00:25:50.814
nokh di khasene, ikh veys nisht, hot zi gevoynt in Bukarest.

00:25:53.030 --> 00:25:55.691
ven ir zent dort geven bahaltn,

00:25:56.270 --> 00:25:58.560
vi azoy hot ir gefilt?

00:25:58.717 --> 00:26:01.884
vo- vos iz geven ayere hargoshes?

00:26:04.876 --> 00:26:07.183
ikh veys aleyn nisht tsu zogn.

00:26:09.061 --> 00:26:11.739
gut hob ikh mikh nisht gekent filn.

00:26:13.482 --> 00:26:15.435
ir zent geven dershrokn?

00:26:15.575 --> 00:26:16.549
vi azoy?

00:26:16.385 --> 00:26:17.713
dershrokn?

00:26:19.068 --> 00:26:22.084
ir zent geven dershrokn? ir hot moyre gehat?

00:26:22.510 --> 00:26:23.147
yo.

00:26:23.894 --> 00:26:25.796
ikh hob gelebt in moyre.

00:26:27.590 --> 00:26:32.479
un varshayndlekh fun dem hob ikh bakumen,

00:26:32.619 --> 00:26:34.385
ikh hob oykh haynt,

00:26:34.576 --> 00:26:35.955
Parkinson.

00:26:37.512 --> 00:26:40.697
fun azoy meyn ikh, fun di moyre.

00:26:41.191 --> 00:26:44.544
az ikh hob gehert az der

00:26:44.836 --> 00:26:48.847
di tir bayn SHAR, makht zikh tsu,

00:26:48.954 --> 00:26:51.398
hob ikh mikh shoyn a shokl gegen,

00:26:51.398 --> 00:26:52.864
nisht vilndik.

00:26:56.412 --> 00:26:57.740
dos iz geven...

00:26:57.577 --> 00:27:00.069
ir zent a mol aroysgegangen fun dort?

00:27:01.239 --> 00:27:03.343
zeyer zeyer veynik.

00:27:04.462 --> 00:27:08.878
un meynstns oyf der nakht, ikh hob gemuzt a bisl aroysgeyn,

00:27:11.195 --> 00:27:14.480
ober zi iz mer mol,

00:27:14.722 --> 00:27:21.534
di froy, gekumen ahin, un zi hot oyfgemakht di tir. dos hot zikh nisht bamerkt.

00:27:21.860 --> 00:27:23.357
az ikh bin dort.

00:27:25.049 --> 00:27:27.795
az ikh zol bakumen a bisl luft.

00:27:28.795 --> 00:27:30.444
geherike luft.

00:27:35.714 --> 00:27:38.240
se iz zeyer a groyse roman.

00:27:42.194 --> 00:27:43.016
un

00:27:43.139 --> 00:27:47.066
ir hot epes gekent dort tun, lezn oder shraybn?

00:27:47.999 --> 00:27:49.817
zi hot dokh nisht gezen.

00:27:50.277 --> 00:27:52.736
se iz geven zeyer a shvakhe

00:27:53.129 --> 00:27:54.896
a shvakhe likht.

00:27:55.998 --> 00:27:58.440
fun vos hot ir geklert a gantsn tog?

00:28:02.394 --> 00:28:03.705
ikh veys nisht.

00:28:09.734 --> 00:28:12.227
koydem hob ikh geklert,

00:28:13.329 --> 00:28:16.007
ikh volt zeyer gevolt khasene hobn.

00:28:16.805 --> 00:28:18.875
ikh bin shoyn nisht geven yung.

00:28:21.040 --> 00:28:22.554
se iz geven

00:28:23.234 --> 00:28:26.182
ikh hob gezen, me hot mikh gezen

00:28:26.845 --> 00:28:27.701
ober,

00:28:28.027 --> 00:28:31.127
ikh hob moyre gehat vegn yidishkeyt.

00:28:31.992 --> 00:28:34.012
az me vet nisht zayn frum.

00:28:34.152 --> 00:28:36.712
vi azoy zol ikh khasene hobn,

00:28:39.215 --> 00:28:42.889
ikh fun a frume shtub, fun frume eltern,

00:28:43.535 --> 00:28:46.258
mit a mentsh vos iz nisht frum.

00:28:46.258 --> 00:28:49.099
neyn, se iz nisht gut, se iz nisht far mir.

00:28:49.171 --> 00:28:50.164
yetst veln mir

00:28:50.164 --> 00:28:52.490
oyf a por minut endikn.
